<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>{ html_head }</head>

{{!-- TODO: 
* license text is currently from an arbitrary package. 
    * Cargo about displays the proper license text for each package, but that wastes a lot of space.
    * but now we may get the license text from source code, and the license text has a "random" copyright holder
    * this change from cargo about seems to stem from the unification with npm
    * I might want to investigat getting a "clean" license text without copyright holders elsewhere
* I might want to expand the list of packages to a table with e.g. author (especially if I dont have a separate license text per author)
* it currently doesn't seem to rebuild correctly whenever needed
* It currently doesnt execute cargo about as part of the build process
* I might want to put this generation behind a feature flag to avoid the need for the PATH dependencies at least
* further unification with the frontend design
--}}

<body class="html-body">
    <main class="container">
        <div class="intro mb-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Third Party Licenses</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">This page lists the licenses of the projects used in shuthost</p>
        </div>
    
        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview of licenses:</h2>
            <ul class="licenses-overview space-y-1">
                {{#each overview}}
                <li><a href="#{{id}}" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">{{name}}</a> ({{count}})</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">All license text:</h2>
            <ul class="licenses-list">
                {{#each licenses}}
                <li class="license border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h3 id="{{id}}" class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">{{name}}</h3>
                    <pre class="license-text bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded text-sm overflow-auto">{{text}}</pre>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-right">Used by:</h4>
                    <ul class="license-used-by">
                        {{#each used_by}}
                        <li><a href="{{#if crate.repository}}{{crate.repository}}{{else}}https://crates.io/crates/{{crate.name}}{{/if}}" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">{{crate.name}} {{crate.version}}</a></li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
